== 遊戲玩法 ==
《金幣大師》的目标是赢得金币来升级道具以建立村庄。<ref name=gameplay>{{Cite web|url=https://moonactive.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/sections/360000924273-Gameplay|title=Gameplay – Coin Master|website=moonactive.zendesk.com|access-date=2020-12-06|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202084358/https://moonactive.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/sections/360000924273-Gameplay|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=koaltion>{{cite web |title=App Trend Games of 2019: Coin Master Tops Charts |url=https://www.thewideinfo.com/coin-master-free-spins/ |date=December 29, 2019  |website=thekoalition.com |publisher=Koalition}}</ref>《金幣大師》可以在应用商店的“冒险游戏”类别中找到，但使用的是赌博机制。为了建造自己的游戏村庄或攻击其他玩家的村庄，用户必须通过[[转盘|转盘]]以赢得虚拟游戏货币。每小时的尝试次数限制为5次，但玩家可以在商店中购买额外的转盘机会和道具。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.spiegel.de/plus/gaming-app-coin-master-wie-kinder-in-der-spielgeldfalle-landen-a-00000000-0002-0001-0000-000165335755|title=Gaming-App Coin Master: Wie Kinder in der Spielgeldfalle landen|work=Spiegel Online|access-date=2020-12-06|archive-date=2019-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116145943/https://www.spiegel.de/plus/gaming-app-coin-master-wie-kinder-in-der-spielgeldfalle-landen-a-00000000-0002-0001-0000-000165335755|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，《金幣大師》还通过其社交频道的链接和订阅电子邮件通讯来提供免费的转盘机会。也有许多网站收集这些链接，让你很容易收集所有的免费礼品奖励。可惜這些謂的獎勵都只是小恩小惠，每次獎勵都只有小量的金幣和轉數。<ref>{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=Coin Master Free Spins - Best CM Strategies|url=https://bestcmstrategies.com/coin-master-free-spins-links/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213094112/https://bestcmstrategies.com/coin-master-free-spins-links/|archive-date=2021-02-13|access-date=2021-01-02|website=Best CM Strategies|language=en-US|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== 策略 ===
玩家可以通过转盘和攻击其他玩家的村庄或掠夺其他玩家来获得财富。不过玩家可以用最多5个盾牌以及宠物犀牛来保护村庄。当玩家的村庄受到攻击时，游戏还允许玩家进行“报复”，这样玩家就可以发起反击。
另一方邊coin master 轉到的機會率十分低，而且沒有轉的時候不斷彈出購賣的廣告，十分煩擾因此大量玩家給予負評<ref name=gameplay/>

=== 关卡 ===
玩家在自己的村庄建好后便会前往下一个村庄。随着玩家的进步，关卡会不断变得更具挑战性。<ref name=iLounge/>到2022年3月，《金币大师》有387个关卡<ref name=villages>{{cite web |title=Villages |url=https://moonactive.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/360011318100-Villages |access-date=December 21, 2020}}</ref>
。

=== 村庄 ===
玩家继续通过超过300个独特主题的村庄冒险游戏，如LA dreams, Buddhist village, Hell's village等等。其他乡村主题包括魔法森林、蒸汽朋克之地和硬币庄园。<ref name=iLounge>{{cite web |title=Coin Master: How The App Lives Up To Its Name |url=https://www.ilounge.com/articles/coin-master-how-the-app-lives-up-to-its-name |date=January 2, 2020 |website=ilounge.com |publisher=iLounge |access-date=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226045021/https://www.ilounge.com/articles/coin-master-how-the-app-lives-up-to-its-name |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=gazettereview>{{cite web |title=Coin Master: How The App Lives Up To Its Name |url=https://gazettereview.com/2019/12/coin-master-taken-casual-gaming-storm-lets-take-look-successful/ |website=gazettereview.com |publisher=Gazette Review |access-date=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303180818/https://gazettereview.com/2019/12/coin-master-taken-casual-gaming-storm-lets-take-look-successful/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>村庄有5种物品，包括人物、宠物、房屋、交通工具和来自自然的物品。<ref name=koaltion/>完成一个村庄你需要硬币。每一个村庄都比前一个更贵。第一个村庄价值310万枚硬币。293村价值超过1.6兆硬币。你可以通过在村庄狂热活动期间建造村庄物品来降低村庄的成本。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Erik|date=2020-09-25|title=How much does a village in Coin Master cost?|url=https://bestcmstrategies.com/how-much-does-a-village-in-coin-master-cost/|access-date=2020-12-11|website=Coin Master Strategies|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226235127/https://bestcmstrategies.com/how-much-does-a-village-in-coin-master-cost/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
=== 卡片收集 ===
游戏中一个非常受欢迎的功能是“卡片收集”。<ref>{{cite web |title=Coin Master Has Taken Casual Gaming by Storm: Let's Take a Look at Why It's Been So Successful |url=https://www.techshout.com/games/2019/29/coin-master-by-moon-active-how-this-game-became-a-sensation-in-2019/ |website=gazettereview.com |publisher=TechShout |access-date=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804165137/https://www.techshout.com/games/2019/29/coin-master-by-moon-active-how-this-game-became-a-sensation-in-2019/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>玩家需要付出巨大的努力去收集和交换卡片，来完成卡片集，这些卡片集可以用来获得奖励，如转盘机会，宠物经验等等。玩家也可以使用金币换取装有可收集卡片的箱子。<ref name=gamenguide/>

卡片的价值各不相同，一些最稀有的卡片很难找到。玩家可以向自己的社区展示最珍贵的纸牌。不過很可惜，當用金幣買魔法寶箱時候，基本上不斷抽到重複無用的卡牌，根據經驗，平均買500個寶箱只有一張是黃金卡牌，因此有大量玩家不滿<ref name=gazettereview/>

世界各地有数不清的在线社交粉丝群专门从事卡片交易。<ref name=gamenguide>{{cite web |title=Predicting the Next Social Game Sensation: How Coin Master Took Us By Surprise |url=https://www.gamenguide.com/articles/101074/20191230/predicting-the-next-social-game-sensation-how-coin-master-took-us-by-surprise.htm |date=January 2, 2020 |website=gamenguide.com |access-date=2021-01-21 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118104600/https://www.gamenguide.com/articles/101074/20191230/predicting-the-next-social-game-sensation-how-coin-master-took-us-by-surprise.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

