此外，每个村庄都有新角色出现。<ref>{{cite web |title=5 Coin Master Tips & Tricks You Need to Know |url=https://heavy.com/games/2019/03/coin-master-game-tips-guide/ |website=heavy.com |publisher=Heavy}}</ref>

